  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras/c62bbc8ec645f0396d06ed25a9c67bc4.avif?t=1758899686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras_big/c62bbc8ec645f0396d06ed25a9c67bc4.avif?t=1758899686 width=1920 height=166 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Deathless</i>, you’ll play as four different heroes, each with their own playstyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VARVARA THE FAIR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras/ebeff6d95ba8a6a9b1e6b21730b73aa9.poster.avif?t=1758899686\" width=620 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras/ebeff6d95ba8a6a9b1e6b21730b73aa9.webm?t=1758899686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras/ebeff6d95ba8a6a9b1e6b21730b73aa9.mp4?t=1758899686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A cunning and clever treasure hunter who excels at manipulating enemy positions on the battlefield.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VASILISA THE WISE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras/79a21b34a76b5aa2674a505ba9db48ab.poster.avif?t=1758899686\" width=620 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras/79a21b34a76b5aa2674a505ba9db48ab.webm?t=1758899686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras/79a21b34a76b5aa2674a505ba9db48ab.mp4?t=1758899686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A powerful elemental sorceress who can summon and dismiss Nursemaids at will to assist her in combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DOBRYNYA NIKITICH</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras/545db853c0912e5c5b1007380c5bba19.poster.avif?t=1758899686\" width=620 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras/545db853c0912e5c5b1007380c5bba19.webm?t=1758899686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras/545db853c0912e5c5b1007380c5bba19.mp4?t=1758899686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The famous hero, equipped with high health and solid defense, making him a master of defensive combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ALYOSHA</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras/e1920f327a11480cfcf88c5f4b5984fd.poster.avif?t=1758899686\" width=620 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras/e1920f327a11480cfcf88c5f4b5984fd.webm?t=1758899686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras/e1920f327a11480cfcf88c5f4b5984fd.mp4?t=1758899686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A warrior from Kitezh. He always carries a sword forged from unique star-steel and a <i>spellbane,</i> a mysterious enchanted wand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras/aef1fda28eedecdb0363cba1e091ec3c.avif?t=1758899686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras_big/aef1fda28eedecdb0363cba1e091ec3c.avif?t=1758899686 width=1920 height=166 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hundreds of card combinations alongside relics provide endless opportunities for creativity — find the most powerful combos to defeat all the bosses and save Belosvet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras/ea94166153254d0ce1fae82cf6130f84.poster.avif?t=1758899686\" width=620 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras/ea94166153254d0ce1fae82cf6130f84.webm?t=1758899686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras/ea94166153254d0ce1fae82cf6130f84.mp4?t=1758899686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras/86c9c578735d080f307d372fc201a927.avif?t=1758899686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras_big/86c9c578735d080f307d372fc201a927.avif?t=1758899686 width=1920 height=166 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete each hero’s quest chain to learn more about the world and the magical creatures that inhabit it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras/c20929102b96e9eb1c1214e77cc586c7.poster.avif?t=1758899686\" width=620 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras/c20929102b96e9eb1c1214e77cc586c7.webm?t=1758899686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras/c20929102b96e9eb1c1214e77cc586c7.mp4?t=1758899686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras/aef1fda28eedecdb0363cba1e091ec3c.avif?t=1758899686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras_big/aef1fda28eedecdb0363cba1e091ec3c.avif?t=1758899686 width=1920 height=166 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After each battle, you’ll decide where to go next. A swamp with a weak enemy or a clearing with a serious foe? The harder the path, the more valuable the reward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each run will offer its own paths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras/ea94166153254d0ce1fae82cf6130f84.poster.avif?t=1758899686\" width=620 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras/ea94166153254d0ce1fae82cf6130f84.webm?t=1758899686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727210/extras/ea94166153254d0ce1fae82cf6130f84.mp4?t=1758899686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
